{"tid":467733,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[史上首見] 椰子蟹獵殺海鷗！","createTime":"2017-11-13T18:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T10:06:09.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ff05517a5887faf8d4f2261ab1f44626b4e9cd","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/InAG_7w0T90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FInAG_7w0T90&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=13b31abb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/InAG_7w0T90</a></div><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國達特茅斯學院（Dartmouth College）研究員萊德爾（Mark Laidre），前往印度洋查戈斯群島（Chagos Islands）觀察椰子蟹生態時，驚見這種陸地上最大的無脊椎甲殼動物，竟然獵殺海鳥並分屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，是史上首次觀察到椰子蟹有獵捕大型脊椎動物的行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/020722_582782f7ab1214a7a2d354e487a18f72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F020722_582782f7ab1214a7a2d354e487a18f72.jpg&h=daafa8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2251086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2251086&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1e678de6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2251086&h=e401b75d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2251086</a></div>"},{"pid":"dfe1618a1a707f668337af2fa1ff77ff93b7bdbd","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:11:45.000Z","msg":"據《衛報》報導，萊德爾透露，當時椰子蟹爬上一棵樹，在靠近地面的樹枝上，襲擊在巢中的海鳥。萊德爾說，螃蟹折斷了鳥兒的翅膀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，迫使牠掉落在地上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，緊接著椰子蟹用鉗抓住海鳥的身體，把牠的另一隻翅膀折斷，讓牠無法動彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"3a02c18bcec98c1f1d87d8743b0d4be544f25da7","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"萊德爾回憶，隨後其他椰子蟹開始聚集，並分屍海鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，現場的景象非常可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。椰子蟹可達四公斤重，身寬可到一公尺。牠們在印度洋和太平洋的珊瑚環礁中很常見，往往可成為附近環境中最大的動物。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/021453_2dd14b07b28913456174a2d001c879e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F021453_2dd14b07b28913456174a2d001c879e1.jpg&h=91fc6f30&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"94e702bca708d5aff4f9ea3aa8bdf148f06dbfba","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"萊德爾計畫在螃蟹洞穴入口處設置攝影機，以便紀錄影像並查明真相。"},{"pid":"10e48418a0e0597184c3a72aab5e514aa6296833","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:20:27.000Z","msg":"有日本科學家表示，椰子蟹的巨鉗夾力可達本身體重的80至100倍，他估計片段中的椰子蟹重約2公斤，可輕易折斷任何鳥類的骨骼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171111/mobile/bknint-20171111123022287-1111_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171111%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171111123022287-1111_17011_001.html&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b87d84f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171111/mobile/bknint-20171111123022287-1111_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1818d595bdbb80864910718b78778631ca65550a","tid":467733,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:20:52.000Z","msg":"算唔算逆轉生物鍊"},{"pid":"6818df4c1a37bf45437f0e5a6679d1a3e5cc0bbb","tid":467733,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算唔算逆轉生物鍊</blockquote><br />\n根本冇既定食物鏈<br />\n邊個嗰一刻強啲就食對方架啦<br />\n<br />\n老鼠都可以食貓"},{"pid":"169ce342bb3382b86d498e7bf78054182cdfc11c","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bca165eb0c55262011a5cd937ada2eee2c32e74","tid":467733,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32020054a0fcb24bb514dd8bb478768bb6abb4ea","tid":467733,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"[兩難決擇]海鷗比巨蟹挾住，救定唔救？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/465187/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/465187/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"f1078ce29400ce8cc6aed6af17847288819a5958","tid":467733,"uid":38395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算唔算逆轉生物鍊</blockquote><br />\n根本冇既定食物鏈<br />\n邊個嗰一刻強啲就食對方架啦<br />\n<br />\n老鼠都可以食貓</blockquote><br />\n蟻多都可以嬲死象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47ed3591bc53a1bc5b64a1d6751b9c60843fdd2","tid":467733,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算唔算逆轉生物鍊</blockquote><br />\n根本冇既定食物鏈<br />\n邊個嗰一刻強啲就食對方架啦<br />\n<br />\n老鼠都可以食貓</blockquote><br />\n蟻多都可以嬲死象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人都可以嬲死男朋友"},{"pid":"13f3d56ff222660f255c5418fcf40bfa933093ac","tid":467733,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited